Package: microTargets
Title: Retrieve microRNA-target Interactions and Compute Correlations
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Julia Perera Bel
Maintainer: Julia Perera Bel <jperera@imim.es>
Description: Retrieve interactions between a set of miRNAs and a set of genes and computes correlations given expression data. The package uses TargetScan v8.0, miRDB v6 and mirTarBase v10.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    openxlsx,
    miRBaseConverter,
    gplots
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
